&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>When you are in a deep sleep &lt;br>
There is no dream, no awareness &lt;br>
of the inside, the mind, and body &lt;br>
And no awareness of the outside world, &lt;br>
the clothes you are wearing, &lt;br>
the bed and place of your sleeping, &lt;br>
the time of your sleep, &lt;br>
persons, relatives friends, foes around you.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>